description_html: These are Spiritual Portraits of characters from Game of Thrones, based on what they do in the fifth season of the series.
story_html:
At the time of this writing, the series is not yet complete. I will be adding more Spiritual Portraits once it does complete.

If a character evolves or changes, I may post an updated image of the personality that results from this growth. Although this is possible, it is highly unlikely.

To learn when I post new images of characters from Game of Thrones and other shows, follow this site on social media or join the SeeOurMinds.com email list!
